    An implementation of the model object 'Line2 T'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Initialized
    • Compond R
    • Control Side
    • Dc Line Control Mode
    • Rectifier Control Mode
    • Inverter Control Mode
    • Operation Mode
    • Meter End
    • Power Demand
